headline: Australia says 52 deaths in London
description: The total death toll from the bomb blasts that tore through packed London underground trains and a bus stands at 52, Australian Prime Minister John Howard said on Friday. (Reuters)
articleBody: The total death toll from the bomb blasts that tore through packed London underground trains and a bus stands at 52, Australian Prime Minister John Howard said on Friday. (Reuters)
